de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.components.processor.results
Class Result

java.lang.Object
  de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.components.processor.results.Result
All Implemented Interfaces:
IResult, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CTMFragment, SimpleResult, XMLFragment
public abstract class Result
extends java.lang.Object
implements IResult

Base implementation of IResult to implement the method providing base functionality. The result represents a row in the result set and contains a number of atomic or complex values like Topics, Associations, CTM- or XTM-strings.

Author:
Sven Krosse
